 but are not required, though\r\nwithout color or stroke colors you'll likely end up with just a circle\r\nvisually!{' '}"},"478":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-12","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#quick-start","content":"Of course it works with different data points too:"},"479":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-13","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#label-options","content":"You can use any string for the `labels` option, and they will be placed in the center of each donut slice."},"480":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-14","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#label-options","content":"Coloring is done via `labelColors`, which takes an array of colors that correspond to the labels. If not provided, the labels will default to white."},"481":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-15","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"Or you can use the `dataLabels` option to show the data values instead of custom labels:"},"482":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-16","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"`labelColors` also is used to color `dataLabels`.{' '}"},"483":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-17","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"The `dataLabels` option also accept `\"percentage\"`:"},"484":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-18","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` option allows you to place a label in the center of the donut chart, which can be used to show a title or other value."},"485":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-19","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"If you set the `centerLabel` option to `\"sum\"` the center label will show the sum of the data values:"},"486":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-20","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"**Adjusting center label styles**"},"487":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-21","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"There are a couple options that allow for adjustment of common title text styles for the center label."},"488":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-22","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontSize`"},"489":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-23","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `32`"},"490":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-24","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontWeight`"},"491":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-25","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `bold`"},"492":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-26","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontFamily`"},"493":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-27","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `monospace`"},"494":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-28","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` will also get a class applied by default that you can use to override the default styling - `\"tmc-pie-center-label\"`."},"495":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-29","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"You can also use the `centerLabelClass` option to add your own class to the center label `<text>` element."},"496":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-30","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#styling","content":"While styling many options is easily achievable with CSS, there are various styling options available for quick & easy use."},"497":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples-31","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/donutchart-examples#size--spacing","content":"The `size` option will change the size of the chart. By default the `size` is `300` which creates a `300px` square, note that all donut charts are squares!"},"498":{"id":"/docs/vanil