mples-1","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#piechart","content":"`piechart`"},"545":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-2","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"Quick Start"},"546":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-3","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#label-options","content":"Label Options"},"547":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-4","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"Data Labels"},"548":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-5","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"Center Label"},"549":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-6","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#styling","content":"Styling"},"550":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-7","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#size--spacing","content":"Size & Spacing"},"551":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-8","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#coloring","content":"Coloring"},"552":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-9","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#piechart","content":"Just a reminder that `piechart` returns an SVG, so you'll want to add it to the DOM."},"553":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-10","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"The most basic possible usage:"},"554":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-11","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"colors are given to make the slices visible, but are not required, though\r\nwithout color or stroke colors you'll likely end up with just a circle\r\nvisually!{' '}"},"555":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-12","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#quick-start","content":"Of course it works with different data points too:"},"556":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-13","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#label-options","content":"You can use any string for the `labels` option, and they will be placed in the center of each pie slice."},"557":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-14","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#label-options","content":"Coloring is done via `labelColors`, which takes an array of colors that correspond to the labels. If not provided, the labels will default to white."},"558":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-15","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"Or you can use the `dataLabels` option to show the data values instead of custom labels:"},"559":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-16","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"`labelColors` also is used to color `dataLabels`.{' '}"},"560":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-17","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#data-labels","content":"The `dataLabels` option also accept `\"percentage\"`:"},"561":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-18","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` option allows you to place a label in the center of the pie chart, which can be used to show a title or other value."},"562":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-19","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"If you set the `centerLabel` option to `\"sum\"` the center label will show the sum of the data values:"},"563":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-20","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"**Adjusting center label styles**"},"564":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-21","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"There are a couple options that allow for adjustment of common title text styles for the center label."},"565":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-22","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontSize`"},"566":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-23","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `32`"},"567":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-24","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontWeight`"},"568":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-25","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `bold`"},"569":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-26","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontFamily`"},"570":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-27","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `monospace`"},"571":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-28","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` will also get a class applied by default that you can use to override the default styling - `\"tmc-pie-center-label\"`."},"572":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-29","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#center-label","content":"You can also use the `centerLabelClass` option to add your own class to the center label `<text>` element."},"573":{"id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples-30","page_id":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/vanilla-examples/piechart-examples#styling","content":"While styling many options is easily achievable with CSS, there are various styling options available for quick & easy use."},"574"